messages.msgSnippet: Great news! A place only 10 minutes from us  does a program for girls my daughter s age. It is a  gymnastics school run by HOMESCHOOL MOMS!Their uniforms are
messages.messageBody:
Great news! A place only 10 minutes from us does a program for girls my
daughter's age. It is a gymnastics school run by HOMESCHOOL MOMS!Their uniforms
are MODEST yet adorable, the cheers are innocent and happy, and the moves are
athletic and pretty, no gyrating or sexual gestures. They learn cheer,
ballet, tumbling, gymnastics, poise and sportsmanship. She starts this week! One
thing that they do on occasion (that made me BURST into tears over) is cheer
for SPECIAL OLYMPICS KIDS!!!!!!! These moms are angels sent from heaven. I am
sooooo relived. I am going to loose sleep at night out of excitement over
her first class!

Adriana
